adelumab, Icatibant', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/176653/', '[1] "Product Information. Gleevec (imatinib mesylate)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Gleevec (imatinib mesylate)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
